title: Chicago and REO Speedwagon - Live at Red Rocks 4Aug14 1080p AC3

Chicago and REO Speedwagon - Live at Red Rocks

Performed at the Red Rocks Amphitheater, Morrison Colorado on August 4, 2014

In 2014 these two legendary rock groups came together to form a Super Group and then went on tour together. This is the forth concert of their 14 date tour. Each group takes the stage individually to play the old songs that made them famous. Then both groups merge together to play even more great music.
